Setup
===============================================================================
SQLITE: http://www.sqlite.org/sqlite-autoconf-3071000.tar.gz
ERLANG: http://www.erlang.org/download/otp_src_R15B.tar.gz

Build and install them.

*On OS-X:* You must -> "./configure CFLAGS="-arch i386" to make it work due to 
a bug in sqlite on OS-X.... that applies to both building Erlang and Sqlite.

Warnings
===============================================================================
Currently, there are some warnings that need to be cleared out, but none of 
them are currently critical.

Notes
===============================================================================
Having "+P 134217727" in the start.sh makes it take up a lot of memory on 
launch to support that many processes... I reduced it to 100k processes for
the time being.

