Console Friendly Quicktests
===============================================================================
Hit the hello world page
    curl http://localhost:8080

Hit the echo page
    curl http://localhost:8080/echo?echo=foobar

Send some invalid json
    curl --data 'echo_json=fofdojaafdadsf' http://localhost:8080/echo_json

Send some valid json
    curl --data 'echo_json={ "testA": "foo" }' http://localhost:8080/echo_json

Send some valid json
    curl -H "X-Winamp-ID: bark" http://localhost:8080/test_headers

Test push
    curl -H "X-Winamp-ID: clientid" --data 'rev=0&translog=[["ADD",{"key":"val"}]]' http://127.0.0.1:8080/push
